#declexample("\

The following code doubles the integer value of each array-cell in a given
array:

#pats2xhtmld_tryit('\
fn doubling{n:nat}
(
  A: &(@[int][n]), n: int n
) :<!wrt> void = let
//
fun loop
  {i:nat | i <= n} .<n-i>.
(
  A: &(@[int][n]), n: int n, i: int i
) :<!wrt> void =
  if n > i then (A[i] := 2 * A[i]; loop (A, n, i+1)) else ()
//
in
  loop (A, n, 0)
end // end of [doubling]
')
")

