The following code implements the standard fold-from-left operation on a
given array:

#pats2xhtmld_tryit('\
fun{
a:t0p}{res:t0p
} array_foldleft{n:int}
(
  A: &(@[a][n])
, asz: size_t n, ini: res, f: (res, a) -> res
